[quote]
[b]Immersive Tool Belt:[/b] Tool belt when you need. Hide when you don't.  
[b]EAC Caveat:[/b] This mod uses custom code that is not compatible with Easy Anti-Cheat (EAC).
[/quote]
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/7daystodie/mods/5649][img]https://github.com/rdok/7dtd_immersive_tool_belt/blob/main/documentation/showcase.gif?raw=true[/img][/url]

[size=5]Features[/size]
[list]
[*] Automatically hides the tool belt three seconds after closing the backpack or switching inventory slots.
[*] Displays the tool belt after three seconds of inactivity when changing a tool belt slot or opening the backpack.
[*] Compatible with controllers and mods like [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/7daystodie/mods/5131]SteelUI - Black UI Theme And Custom HUD[/url]
[*] 7daystodie Version: 1.0 (b333)
[*] Install with [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/about/vortex/]Vortex[/url].
[/list]
